# skillspec tooling artifacts — NOT read by Claude Code, ignored from version control.
# Claude's skill loader only reads SKILL.md (+ references/ linked from it). The files
# below exist solely for the `skillspec` CLI (contract, dependency ledger, import
# scaffolding) and have zero effect on how the skills run in Claude. Regenerate any
# time with `skillspec import-skill`.
**/skill.spec.yml
**/deps.toml
**/source/
**/imports/
**/resources/
**/.skillspec/

# NOTE: references/ is intentionally NOT ignored — those files are linked from SKILL.md
# and load on demand in Claude, so they affect skill behavior and must be committed.

# Local Claude Code settings (machine-specific permissions/state — never shared)
.claude/settings.local.json

# Generated SkillSpec doctor report (regenerable; not read by Claude)
SKILLSPEC-REPORT.md

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Rust build output (if skillspec is built from source in-tree)
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
